Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_qlm::_cfg

Notes: Certain QLM_SPD is valid only for certain QLM_CFG configuration, refer to HRM for valid combinations. These csrs are reset only on COLD_RESET. The Reset values for QLM_SPD and QLM_CFG are as follows: MIO_QLM0_CFG SPD=F, CFG=2 SGMII (AGX0) MIO_QLM1_CFG SPD=0, CFG=1 PCIE 2x1 (PEM0/PEM1)
